OL,3,CDumfries & Galloway woman pays for
OL,4,Coperation in France due to NHS waiting
OL,5,Ctimes
OL,7,FA Dumfries and Galloway woman left the
OL,8,FUnited Kingdom to go and get a hip
OL,9,Freplacement due to extremely long
OL,10,Fwaiting times on the NHS.
OL,12,FKathryn Veryecken was diagnosed with
OL,13,Fsevere arthritis in her hip and was
OL,14,Ftold that she should expect up to 18
OL,15,Fmonths for surgery on the NHS.
OL,17,FShe paid less than a private operation
OL,18,Fin the UK for the treatment and
OL,19,Ftravelled to France because it would
OL,20,Fbe quicker than waiting for the
OL,21,Foperation on the NHS.
