OL,5,Ctimes
OL,7,FIn Dumfries and Galloway the average
OL,8,Fwaiting time for hip replacements at
OL,9,Fthe end of last year was 30 weeks.
OL,11,FWhen asked NHS Dumfries and Galloway
OL,12,Fsaid it can not comment on individual
OL,13,Fpatients.
