OL,3,CDumfries & Galloway woman pays for
OL,4,Coperation in France due to NHS waiting
OL,5,Ctimes
OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV Border before her
OL,8,Fsurgery, Kathryn said: "I was
OL,9,Fdiagnosed with severe arthritis in my
OL,10,Fhip and was told I needed a total hip
OL,11,Freplacement. That then led me to see
OL,12,Fsomeone at the hospital and I was put
OL,13,Fon a waiting list. The waiting list I
OL,14,Fwas told would be between 15 and 18
OL,15,Fmonths.
OL,17,F"I live in Dumfries and Galloway which
OL,18,Fis one of the really beautiful parts
OL,19,Fof the country with walks all around
OL,20,Fhere and I really struggle to walk to
OL,21,Fthe shops.
