OL,3,CDumfries & Galloway woman pays for
OL,4,Coperation in France due to NHS waiting
OL,5,Ctimes
OL,7,F"I want to be able to enjoy where I
OL,8,Flive and just going for a simple thing
OL,9,Flike a stroll in the country."
OL,11,FKathryn then went via a company in
OL,12,FGlasgow to get surgery in France to
OL,13,Ftreat her hip.
OL,15,FShe and her husband were there for
OL,16,Falmost three weeks and when we spoke
OL,17,Fto her on her return to Dumfries and
OL,18,FGalloway, she felt as though it was
OL,19,Fmoney well spent.
