OL,3,CDumfries & Galloway woman pays for
OL,4,Coperation in France due to NHS waiting
OL,5,Ctimes
OL,7,FKathryn said: "I am feeling positive
OL,8,Fand improving each and every day. I
OL,9,Fcan walk round the house now without
OL,10,Fany support.
OL,12,F"I absolutely support the NHS, I think
OL,13,Fit is one of the most valuable things
OL,14,Fwe have in the UK.
OL,16,F"It has been underfunded for so long
OL,17,Fand I am in a fortunate position that
OL,18,FI can pay that money, I don't think I
OL,19,Fshould have to but health, money,
OL,20,Fhealth comes first doesn't it."
